### Variablen
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3145
@authToken = your-auth-token-here

### Authentifizierung

# Register neuen User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123456",
  "isArtist": false
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "test123456"
}

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Locations

# Neue Location erstellen
POST {{baseUrl}}/locations
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Olympiapark München",
  "description": "Berühmter Park und Veranstaltungsort",
  "address": "Spiridon-Louis-Ring 21, 80809 München",
  "latitude": 48.1755,
  "longitude": 11.5517,
  "logoUrl": "https://example.com/logo.jpg",
  "website": "https://www.olympiapark.de",
  "socialMediaLinks": {
    "instagram": "https://instagram.com/olympiapark",
    "facebook": "https://facebook.com/olympiapark"
  }
}

# Location by ID abrufen
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations/123
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

# Location folgen
POST {{baseUrl}}/locations/123/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Events

# Event erstellen
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/create
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sommerfestival 2024",
  "description": "Das größte Sommerfestival in München",
  "startDate": "2024-07-15",
  "startTime": "18:00",
  "locationId": "123",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/event.jpg"
}

# Event-Bild hochladen
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/upload/event-image
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="event.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./event.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

# Events in der Nähe finden
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/nearby?lat=48.1351&lon=11.5820&distance=5
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

# Events nach Kategorie
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/category/music?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

# Favorisierte Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/favorites?ids=123,456,789
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Suche

# Events suchen
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/search?query=festival&location=München
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

# Locations suchen
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations/search?query=park
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

